      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-orange-200">
      <ul>
        <li>Username: JuanM</li>
        <li>Average of Tokens sold per month: 100EPMT(inventado)</li>
        <li>Average price: 380000 COP</li>
        <li>Main energy source: Wind</li>
        <li>etc</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-orange-200">
      <ul>
        <li>Username: DiegoB-UdeA</li>
        <li>Average of Tokens sold per month: 10EPMT(inventado)</li>
        <li>Average price: 100000 COP</li>
